### Sertifikat API Testing & Documentation
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:3000
@apiPrefix = /api/dashboard

###############################################################################
### CURRENT IMPLEMENTATION
###############################################################################

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Default: Top 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/sertifikat-per-skema
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Top 50)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/sertifikat-per-skema?limit=50
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Filter tahun 2025)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/sertifikat-per-skema?tahun=2025
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Sertifikat Per Skema (Sort ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/sertifikat-per-skema?sort=asc&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###############################################################################
### BACKEND REQUEST - ADDITIONAL FIELDS NEEDED
###############################################################################

### REQUEST: Tambahkan field berikut ke response API /api/dashboard/sertifikat-per-skema
### 
### Current Response Structure:
### {
###   "data": [
###     {
###       "id_skema": 379,
###       "kode_skema": "SKK-36-10/2024",
###       "skema": "Pemasaran Digital",
###       "kategori": "DIGITAL MARKETING AND IT FUNDAMENTAL",
###       "total_pemegang": 7631
###     }
###   ],
###   "meta": {
###     "total_skema": 10,
###     "total_pemegang_sertifikat": 30948,
###     "tahun_filter": null,
###     "limit": 10
###   }
### }
###
### REQUESTED ADDITIONS TO META:
### {
###   "meta": {
###     "total_skema": 10,
###     "total_pemegang_sertifikat": 30948,
###     "tahun_filter": null,
###     "limit": 10,
###     
###     // NEW FIELDS NEEDED:
###     "periode": "Mei 2026",                    // Format: "Bulan Tahun" (dinamis berdasarkan data terbaru)
###     "tanggal_update": "2026-05-28",           // Tanggal terakhir data diupdate
###     
###     "trends": {
###       "total_pemegang_sertifikat": {
###         "current": 30948,                     // Total saat ini
###         "previous": 28500,                    // Total periode sebelumnya (bulan lalu)
###         "percentage": 8.6,                    // Persentase perubahan
###         "direction": "up",                    // "up", "down", atau "stable"
###         "formatted": "+8.6%"                  // Format untuk display
###       },
###       "total_skema": {
###         "current": 50,
###         "previous": 48,
###         "percentage": 4.2,
###         "direction": "up",
###         "formatted": "+4.2%"
###       }
###     }
###   }
### }
###
### LOGIC FOR TRENDS:
### - Compare current month data with previous month
### - Calculate percentage: ((current - previous) / previous) * 100
### - Direction: "up" if positive, "down" if negative, "stable" if 0
### - Formatted: Add "+" for positive, "-" for negative, "+0.0%" for stable
###
### USE CASE:
### - Display "Data diambil per [periode]" instead of hardcoded "Mei 2026"
### - Show growth indicators in summary cards (e.g., "+8.6%" with up arrow)
### - Provide context about data freshness to users
###

###############################################################################
### REQUEST: New Endpoint for Sertifikat Summary
###############################################################################

### ENDPOINT: GET /api/dashboard/sertifikat-summary
### 
### Expected Response:
### {
###   "data": {
###     "total_pemegang_sertifikat": 39360,
###     "total_skema": 50,
###     "top_skema": {
###       "id_skema": 379,
###       "skema": "Pemasaran Digital",
###       "total_pemegang": 7631
###     },
###     "trends": {
###       "pemegang_sertifikat": {
###         "percentage": 15.7,
###         "direction": "up",
###         "formatted": "+15.7%"
###       },
###       "skema": {
###         "percentage": 16.8,
###         "direction": "up",
###         "formatted": "+16.8%"
###       }
###     }
###   },
###   "meta": {
###     "periode": "Mei 2026",
###     "comparison_period": "April 2026",
###     "tanggal_update": "2026-05-28"
###   }
### }
###
### LOGIC:
### - total_pemegang_sertifikat: Sum of all certificate holders across all schemas
### - total_skema: Count of active schemas
### - top_skema: Schema with highest total_pemegang
### - trends: Compare with previous month data
###

###############################################################################
### REQUEST: Search/Filter Endpoint for Certificate Holders
###############################################################################

### ENDPOINT: GET /api/sertifikat/search
### 
### Query Parameters:
### - q: Search query (nama pemegang, nomor sertifikat)
### - skema: Filter by skema name
### - kategori: Filter by kategori
### - status: Filter by status (aktif, kadaluarsa, akan_kadaluarsa)
### - limit: Number of results (default: 20)
### - offset: Pagination offset (default: 0)
###
### Expected Response:
### {
###   "data": [
###     {
###       "id": 1,
###       "skema": "Pemasaran Digital",
###       "pemegang": "Ahmad Rizki",
###       "nomor_sertifikat": "CERT-2025-001",
###       "tanggal_terbit": "2025-01-15",
###       "tanggal_berlaku": "2028-01-15",
###       "status": "aktif",
###       "kategori": "DIGITAL MARKETING AND IT FUNDAMENTAL",
###       "institusi": "LSP Digital Indonesia"
###     }
###   ],
###   "meta": {
###     "total": 150,
###     "limit": 20,
###     "offset": 0,
###     "has_more": true
###   }
### }
###
### USE CASE:
### - Search functionality in sertifikat screen
### - Filter by skema/kategori dropdown
### - Display individual certificate holder details
###

